//
// Single machine-readable agent manifest.
//
// Format:
//   SB_AGENT_MANIFEST_ENTRY(type_id, deployment, scope, authority, activation)
//
// `type_id`, `deployment`, `authority`, and `activation` are tokens. `scope` is
// a string literal. This file is included by the runtime manifest builder and
// parsed by the AEIC manifest drift gate; do not duplicate canonical agent
// identity lists elsewhere without adding a gate comparison.

